<title>Search for a contact</title>

<if:choose>
<if:when test="platform:unity"></if:when>
  <p>You can search for an online contact in one of two ways:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>In the <gui>Activities</gui> overview, start typing the name of the
      contact.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Matching contacts will appear in the overview instead of the usual list
      of applications.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press <key>Enter</key> to select the contact at the top of the list or
      click the contact that you want to select if they are not at the
      top.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>
</if:choose>

  <p>To search from inside <app>Contacts</app>:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Click inside the search field.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Start typing the name of the contact.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

